@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Refresh Countries - Fetch and cache all countries
POST {{baseUrl}}/countries/refresh

### 2. Get All Countries
GET {{baseUrl}}/countries

### 3. Get Countries - Filter by Region
GET {{baseUrl}}/countries?region=Africa

### 4. Get Countries - Filter by Currency
GET {{baseUrl}}/countries?currency=NGN

### 5. Get Countries - Sort by GDP (Descending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/countries?sort=gdp_desc

### 6. Get Countries - Sort by GDP (Ascending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/countries?sort=gdp_asc

### 7. Get Countries - Sort by Population (Descending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/countries?sort=population_desc

### 8. Get Countries - Sort by Name (Ascending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/countries?sort=name_asc

### 9. Get Countries - Combined Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/countries?region=Africa&sort=gdp_desc

### 10. Get Single Country by Name
GET {{baseUrl}}/countries/Nigeria

### 11. Get Another Country
GET {{baseUrl}}/countries/Ghana

### 12. Get Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/countries/status

### 13. Get Summary Image
GET {{baseUrl}}/countries/image

### 14. Delete a Country
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/countries/Nigeria

### 15. Try to Get Deleted Country (Should return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/countries/Nigeria
